<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="ja"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"><title>Claude Code CLI Cheatsheet</title><link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>:root{--bg:#ffffff;--surface:#f8f9fa;--surface2:#e9ecef;--border:#dee2e6;--accent:#e8774a;--accent2:#5b8dee;--accent3:#4ecdc4;--accent4:#6f91b3;--text:#1a1a1a;--text-muted:#6b7280;--text-dim:#495057;--green:#10b981;--yellow:#f59e0b;--code-bg:#f0f3f5}body.dark-mode{--bg:#0a0c10;--surface:#111318;--surface2:#181c24;--border:#1e2430;--accent:#e8774a;--accent2:#5b8dee;--accent3:#4ecdc4;--accent4:#7da0c3;--text:#e2e8f0;--text-muted:#9ca3af;--text-dim:#94a3b8;--green:#34d399;--yellow:#fbbf24;--code-bg:#0d1117}*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden}body::before{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(94,130,220,.08) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(94,130,220,.08) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:40px 40px;pointer-events:none;z-index:0}body.dark-mode::before{background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(94,130,220,.04) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(94,130,220,.04) 1px,transparent 1px)}.container{max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 24px 80px;position:relative;z-index:1}header{text-align:center;margin-bottom:56px}.badge{display:inline-block;background:rgba(232,119,74,.12);border:1px solid rgba(232,119,74,.3);color:var(--accent);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:2px;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;margin-bottom:16px;text-transform:uppercase}h1{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,60px);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-1px;line-height:1.1;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent) 0%,#ff8554 50%,var(--accent) 100%);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;margin-bottom:12px}body.dark-mode h1{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent) 0%,var(--accent) 50%,#d53a1c 100%);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text}.subtitle{color:var(--text-muted);font-size:14px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;letter-spacing:.5px}.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(360px,1fr));gap:16px}.grid-wide{grid-column:1 / -1}.card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;transition:border-color .2s,transform .2s}.card:hover{border-color:rgba(232,119,74,.25);transform:translateY(-2px)}.card-header{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:14px 18px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface2)}.card-icon{font-size:16px;line-height:1}.card-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-dim)}.card-body{padding:16px 18px}.cmd-list{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}.cmd-item{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto;gap:8px;align-items:start;padding:8px 10px;background:var(--code-bg);border-radius:4px;border:1px solid transparent;transition:border-color .15s}.cmd-item:hover{border-color:var(--border)}.cmd-item.has-desc{grid-template-columns:1fr}code{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;color:var(--green);line-height:1.6}code .flag{color:var(--accent2)}code .arg{color:var(--accent)}code .comment{color:var(--text-muted)}code .str{color:var(--yellow)}.desc{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;line-height:1.5;margin-top:3px}.kbd-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:6px}.kbd-item{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:8px;padding:7px 10px;background:var(--code-bg);border-radius:4px;border:1px solid transparent}.kbd-item:hover{border-color:var(--border)}.kbd-label{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-dim);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}kbd{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;white-space:nowrap}kbd span{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:2px solid rgba(0,0,0,.1);color:var(--text);padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;font-size:10px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.05)}body.dark-mode kbd span{border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);border-bottom:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);box-shadow:none}table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px}thead th{padding:8px 12px;text-align:left;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-muted);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}tbody tr{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);transition:background .1s}tbody tr:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.02)}tbody tr:last-child{border-bottom:none}td{padding:9px 12px;vertical-align:top;line-height:1.5}td:first-child code{color:var(--accent4)}td:last-child{color:var(--text-muted)}.slash{color:var(--accent)}.section-label{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:12px;font-weight:600;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}.section-label::after{content:'';flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--border)}.code-block{background:var(--code-bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:14px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;line-height:1.8;overflow-x:auto}.code-block .line-comment{color:var(--text-muted);font-style:italic}.code-block .line-cmd{color:var(--green)}.code-block .line-flag{color:var(--accent2)}.code-block .line-val{color:var(--yellow)}.tag{display:inline-block;font-size:9px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;padding:1px 6px;border-radius:2px;font-weight:500;margin-left:6px;vertical-align:middle;letter-spacing:.5px}.tag-new{background:rgba(52,211,153,.15);color:var(--green);border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.3)}.tag-pro{background:rgba(251,191,36,.15);color:var(--yellow);border:1px solid rgba(251,191,36,.3)}.tag-danger{background:rgba(239,68,68,.15);color:#f87171;border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.3)}footer{text-align:center;margin-top:56px;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted)}footer a{color:var(--accent2);text-decoration:none}footer a:hover{text-decoration:underline}.dot{color:var(--accent);margin:0 8px}.theme-toggle{position:fixed;top:20px;right:20px;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;padding:8px 16px;cursor:pointer;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;color:var(--text);transition:all .2s;z-index:100;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}.theme-toggle:hover{border-color:var(--accent);transform:scale(1.05)}.os-tabs{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:24px}.os-tab{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:8px 20px;cursor:pointer;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text-muted);transition:all .2s;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px}.os-tab:hover{border-color:var(--accent2);color:var(--text)}.os-tab.active{background:var(--accent2);border-color:var(--accent2);color:white}.os-content{display:none}.os-content.active{display:block}@media (max-width:768px){.kbd-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.theme-toggle{top:10px;right:10px;font-size:11px;padding:6px 12px}.os-tabs{flex-direction:column}}</style>
</head><body><button class="theme-toggle" id="themeToggle"><span id="themeIcon">🌙</span><span id="themeText">Dark</span></button><div class="container"><header><div class="badge">Cross-Platform CLI Reference</div><h1>Claude Code Cheatsheet</h1><p class="subtitle">$ claude --version &nbsp;·&nbsp; Updated March 2026</p></header><div class="section-label">セットアップ &amp; 起動</div><div class="grid" style="margin-bottom:16px"><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">⚡</span><span class="card-title">インストール</span></div><div class="card-body"><div class="code-block"><div><span class="line-comment"># 公式インストーラー（推奨）</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">curl -sL https://install.anthropic.com | sh</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># npm でインストール</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># バージョン確認</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">claude <span class="line-flag">--version</span></span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># 最新版にアップデート</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">claude update</span></div></div></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">🚀</span><span class="card-title">起動パターン</span></div><div class="card-body"><ul class="cmd-list"><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code>claude</code><div class="desc">インタラクティブREPLを起動</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code>claude <span class="str">"プロジェクトを要約して"</span></code><div class="desc">初期プロンプト付きで起動</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code>claude <span class="flag">-p</span><span class="str">"関数を説明して"</span></code><div class="desc">結果を表示して即終了（Print mode）</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code>claude <span class="flag">-c</span></code><div class="desc">直近の会話を継続</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code>claude <span class="flag">-r</span><span class="arg">abc123</span><span class="str">"続き"</span></code><div class="desc">セッションIDで再開</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code>claude <span class="flag">--continue</span></code><div class="desc">前回セッションを継続</div></li></ul></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">⌨️</span><span class="card-title">キーボードショートカット</span></div><div class="card-body"><div class="os-tabs"><button class="os-tab active" data-os="mac">🍎 macOS</button><button class="os-tab" data-os="windows">🪟 Windows</button><button class="os-tab" data-os="linux">🐧 Linux</button></div><div class="os-content active" data-os="mac"><div class="kbd-grid"><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">操作キャンセル</span><kbd><span>Ctrl</span><span>C</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">終了</span><kbd><span>Ctrl</span><span>D</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">オートコンプリート</span><kbd><span>Tab</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">コマンド履歴</span><kbd><span>↑</span></kbd><kbd><span>↓</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">複数行入力</span><kbd><span>Shift</span><span>Enter</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">送信</span><kbd><span>Enter</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">行頭へ移動</span><kbd><span>Ctrl</span><span>A</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">行末へ移動</span><kbd><span>Ctrl</span><span>E</span></kbd></div></div></div><div class="os-content" data-os="windows"><div class="kbd-grid"><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">操作キャンセル</span><kbd><span>Ctrl</span><span>C</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">終了</span><kbd><span>Ctrl</span><span>D</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">オートコンプリート</span><kbd><span>Tab</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">コマンド履歴</span><kbd><span>↑</span></kbd><kbd><span>↓</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">複数行入力</span><kbd><span>Shift</span><span>Enter</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">送信</span><kbd><span>Enter</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">行頭へ移動</span><kbd><span>Home</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">行末へ移動</span><kbd><span>End</span></kbd></div></div></div><div class="os-content" data-os="linux"><div class="kbd-grid"><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">操作キャンセル</span><kbd><span>Ctrl</span><span>C</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">終了</span><kbd><span>Ctrl</span><span>D</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">オートコンプリート</span><kbd><span>Tab</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">コマンド履歴</span><kbd><span>↑</span></kbd><kbd><span>↓</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">複数行入力</span><kbd><span>Shift</span><span>Enter</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">送信</span><kbd><span>Enter</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">行頭へ移動</span><kbd><span>Ctrl</span><span>A</span></kbd></div><div class="kbd-item"><span class="kbd-label">行末へ移動</span><kbd><span>Ctrl</span><span>E</span></kbd></div></div></div><div style="margin-top:10px; padding:8px 10px; background:var(--code-bg); border-radius:4px; font-size:11px; color:var(--text-muted); font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;">💡 /terminal-setup でShift+Enter複数行を有効化 </div></div></div></div><div class="section-label">スラッシュコマンド（セッション内）</div><div class="grid" style="margin-bottom:16px"><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">📋</span><span class="card-title">基本スラッシュコマンド</span></div><div class="card-body"><table><thead><tr><th>コマンド</th><th>説明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/help</span></code></td><td>ヘルプ・使用可能コマンド表示</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/exit</span></code></td><td>REPLを終了</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/clear</span></code></td><td>会話履歴・コンテキストをリセット</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/compact</span>[指示]</code></td><td>会話を要約してコンテキスト節約</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/config</span></code></td><td>設定パネルを開く</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/doctor</span></code></td><td>インストール状態を診断</td></tr><tr><td><code>/fast </code></td><td>高速出力モード切替（<strong>Opus 4.6専用・最大2.5倍速</strong>・同じ知能・プレミアム料金 $30/$150/MTok）</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/model</span></code></td><td>使用モデルを切り替え</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/effort</span>[low|high]</code></td><td>Opus/Sonnet 4.6の思考深度を制御（low=高速、high=深い推論）</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/plan</span></code></td><td>Plan Modeを起動（実装前に計画を立てて確認）</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/rewind</span></code></td><td>会話のみ・またはコードも含めて選択的ロールバック</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/debug</span></code></td><td>セッションのデバッグ情報を表示</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/sessions</span></code></td><td>セッション一覧・管理</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/permissions</span></code></td><td>ツール権限を設定</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/memory</span></code></td><td>メモリの表示・編集</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/usage</span></code></td><td>トークン使用量・コスト確認</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/theme</span></code></td><td>カラーテーマ変更</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/review</span></code></td><td>直近の変更をコードレビュー</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/todos</span></code></td><td>TODOリスト表示</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/mcp</span></code></td><td>MCPサーバー管理</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">/ide</span></code></td><td>IDE統合管理</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">🎛️</span><span class="card-title">CLIフラグ</span></div><div class="card-body"><table><thead><tr><th>フラグ</th><th>説明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code><span class="slash">-p</span>, <span class="slash">--print</span></code></td><td>結果表示して終了（非対話）</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">-c</span>, <span class="slash">--continue</span></code></td><td>直近の会話を継続</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">-r</span>&lt;id&gt;</code></td><td>指定セッションIDで再開</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">--from-pr</span>&lt;PR番号&gt;</code></td><td>PRに紐づいたセッションを再開 <span class="tag tag-new">NEW</span></td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">--model</span>&lt;モデル名&gt;</code></td><td>使用モデル指定</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">--max-turns</span>&lt;n&gt;</code></td><td>最大ターン数制限</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">--add-dir</span>&lt;パス&gt;</code></td><td>追加ディレクトリを参照</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">--verbose</span></code></td><td>詳細ログを表示</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">--output-format</span></code></td><td>出力形式（text/json/stream-json）</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">--allowedTools</span></code></td><td>許可ツールを明示指定</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">--disallowedTools</span></code></td><td>禁止ツールを指定</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">--system-prompt</span></code></td><td>システムプロンプトを完全置換（デフォルト指示が消える）</td></tr><tr><td><code><span class="slash">--append-system-prompt</span></code></td><td>システムプロンプトを追記（デフォルト維持・通常はこちら推奨）</td></tr><tr><td><code>--dangerously-skip-permissions </code></td><td>権限確認をすべてスキップ（危険: 開発用途のみ推奨）</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div><div class="section-label">モデル・パイプ・MCP</div><div class="grid" style="margin-bottom:16px"><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">🤖</span><span class="card-title">モデル選択</span></div><div class="card-body"><table><thead><tr><th>モデル</th><th>用途</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>claude-sonnet-4-6 </code></td><td>標準的な用途向けのバランス型。多くのプランでデフォルト</td></tr><tr><td><code>claude-haiku-4-5 </code></td><td>高速・低コスト。簡単なタスクやバッチ処理向け</td></tr><tr><td><code>claude-opus-4-6 </code></td><td>最新・最高性能。複雑な推論・長時間エージェント・重要な本番タスク向け</td></tr></tbody></table><div style="margin-top:10px" class="code-block"><div><span class="line-comment"># 起動時にモデル指定</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">claude <span class="line-flag">--model</span><span class="line-val">claude-opus-4-6</span></span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># セッション中に切り替え</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">/model</span></div></div></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">🔗</span><span class="card-title">パイプ・スクリプト連携</span></div><div class="card-body"><div class="code-block"><div><span class="line-comment"># ファイルをパイプで渡す</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">cat error.log | claude <span class="line-flag">-p</span><span class="line-val">"原因を特定して"</span></span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># git ログを要約</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">git log <span class="line-flag">--oneline</span>| claude <span class="line-flag">-p</span><span class="line-val">"変更を要約"</span></span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># JSON形式で出力</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">claude <span class="line-flag">-p</span><span class="line-flag">--output-format</span>json <span class="line-val">"分析して"</span>&gt; result.json</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># 複数処理のスクリプト化</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">claude <span class="line-flag">-p</span><span class="line-val">"コードを分析"</span><span class="line-flag">--max-turns</span>5 <span class="line-flag">--output-format</span>text &gt; analysis.txt</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># ディレクトリ構造を説明</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">ls <span class="line-flag">-la</span>| claude <span class="line-flag">-p</span><span class="line-val">"構造を説明して"</span></span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># 画像・PDFファイルを読み込み</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">claude <span class="line-val">"この画像を説明して"</span>&lt; screenshot.png</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">claude <span class="line-flag">-p</span><span class="line-val">"PDFを要約"</span><span class="line-flag">--attach</span>report.pdf</span></div></div></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">🔌</span><span class="card-title">MCPサーバー管理</span></div><div class="card-body"><div class="code-block"><div><span class="line-comment"># MCPサーバーを追加（stdio）</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">claude mcp add <span class="line-flag">--transport</span>stdio &lt;name&gt; -- &lt;cmd&gt;</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># 環境変数付きで追加</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">claude mcp add <span class="line-flag">--transport</span>stdio supabase \</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="line-flag">--env</span>SUPABASE_ACCESS_TOKEN=&lt;token&gt; \</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">&nbsp;&nbsp;-- npx -y @supabase/mcp-server-supabase</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># MCPサーバー一覧</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">claude mcp list</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># セッション内でMCPを管理</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">/mcp</span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="section-label">設定・カスタマイズ</div><div class="grid" style="margin-bottom:16px"><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">🚫</span><span class="card-title">.claudeignore ファイル</span></div><div class="card-body"><div class="code-block"><div><span class="line-comment"># プロジェクトルートに .claudeignore を作成</span></div><div><span class="line-comment"># 大規模プロジェクトでスキャン対象を制限</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-val">node_modules/</span></div><div><span class="line-val">dist/</span></div><div><span class="line-val">build/</span></div><div><span class="line-val">*.log</span></div><div><span class="line-val">.env</span></div><div><span class="line-val">.env.*</span></div><div><span class="line-val">coverage/</span></div><div><span class="line-val">*.min.js</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># コスト削減・処理速度UP</span></div></div></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">🔐</span><span class="card-title">環境変数設定</span></div><div class="card-body"><div class="code-block"><div><span class="line-comment"># ~/.zshrc または ~/.bashrc に追記</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-cmd">export</span><span class="line-val">ANTHROPIC_API_KEY</span>=<span class="line-str">"sk-ant-..."</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">export</span><span class="line-val">ANTHROPIC_MODEL</span>=<span class="line-str">"claude-sonnet-4-6"</span></div><div><span class="line-comment"># モデル別に固定する場合</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">export</span><span class="line-val">ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_OPUS_MODEL</span>=<span class="line-str">"claude-opus-4-6"</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">export</span><span class="line-val">ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_SONNET_MODEL</span>=<span class="line-str">"claude-sonnet-4-6"</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">export</span><span class="line-val">ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_HAIKU_MODEL</span>=<span class="line-str">"claude-haiku-4-5"</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># プロジェクト固有の設定</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">export</span><span class="line-val">CLAUDE_PROJECT_PATH</span>=<span class="line-str">"/path/to/project"</span></div></div></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">📝</span><span class="card-title">CLAUDE.md 設定例</span></div><div class="card-body"><div class="code-block"><div><span class="line-comment"># プロジェクト用: .claude/CLAUDE.md</span></div><div><span class="line-comment"># グローバル用: ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment">## コーディング規約</span></div><div><span class="line-val">- TypeScriptを使用すること</span></div><div><span class="line-val">- React Hooks + 関数コンポーネント</span></div><div><span class="line-val">- テストはJestで記述</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment">## アーキテクチャ</span></div><div><span class="line-val">- Frontend: Next.js</span></div><div><span class="line-val">- Backend: Node.js / Express</span></div><div><span class="line-val">- DB: PostgreSQL + Prisma</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment">## ファイル構成</span></div><div><span class="line-val">- components: src/components/</span></div><div><span class="line-val">- utils: src/utils/</span></div></div></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">🔒</span><span class="card-title">権限・ツール制御</span></div><div class="card-body"><div class="code-block"><div><span class="line-comment"># 特定ツールのみ許可</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">claude <span class="line-flag">--allowedTools</span><span class="line-val">"Bash(git:*)" "Write" "Read"</span></span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># 危険なコマンドを禁止</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">claude <span class="line-flag">--disallowedTools</span><span class="line-val">"Bash(rm:*)" "Bash(sudo:*)"</span></span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># settings.json で永続設定</span></div><div><span class="line-val">{</span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp;"permissions":{</span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"allowedTools": ["Read", "Write", "Bash(git *)"],</span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"deny": ["Read(./.env)", "Write(./prod.*)"]</span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp}</span></div><div><span class="line-val">}</span></div></div></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">🛠️</span><span class="card-title">カスタムコマンド</span></div><div class="card-body"><div class="code-block"><div><span class="line-comment"># プロジェクト共有: .claude/commands/</span></div><div><span class="line-comment"># 個人用: ~/.claude/commands/</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># 例: .claude/commands/debug.md</span></div><div><span class="line-val">---</span></div><div><span class="line-val">description: デバッグ用コマンド</span></div><div><span class="line-val">model: claude-opus-4-5</span></div><div><span class="line-val">---</span></div><div><span class="line-val">エラーを詳細に分析し原因と修正案を提示</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># セッション内で呼び出し</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">/debug</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">/test</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">/deploy</span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="section-label">上級テクニック</div><div class="grid" style="margin-bottom:16px"><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">🌿</span><span class="card-title">Git Worktree 並列作業</span></div><div class="card-body"><div class="code-block"><div><span class="line-comment"># 機能ブランチを並列で作業</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">git worktree add ../app-auth <span class="line-flag">-b</span>feature/auth main</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">git worktree add ../app-api <span class="line-flag">-b</span>feature/api main</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># 各ディレクトリで独立したClaude</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">cd ../app-auth && claude</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">cd ../app-api && claude</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># 実験用ブランチ（失敗してもOK）</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">git worktree add ../experiment <span class="line-flag">-b</span>exp/refactor</span></div><div><span class="line-comment"># 失敗したらディレクトリごと削除</span></div></div></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">🤝</span><span class="card-title">サブエージェント <span class="tag tag-new">NEW</span></span></div><div class="card-body"><div class="code-block"><div><span class="line-comment"># --agents フラグで専門エージェントを定義</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">claude <span class="line-flag">--agents</span><span class="line-val">'{'</span></span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp;"code-reviewer":{</span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"description": "コード変更後に自動レビュー",</span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"prompt": "シニアエンジニアとしてレビュー",</span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"tools": ["Read", "Grep", "Glob"],</span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"model": "sonnet"</span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp}</span></div><div><span class="line-val"><span class="line-cmd">}'</span></span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># スキルファイルでモデル呼び出し型の機能追加</span></div><div><span class="line-comment"># ~/.claude/skills/ または .claude/skills/</span></div></div></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">🔄</span><span class="card-title">Hooks（自動化）</span></div><div class="card-body"><div class="code-block"><div><span class="line-comment"># settings.json でフック設定</span></div><div><span class="line-val">{</span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp;"hooks":{</span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"PostToolUse": [{</span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"matcher": "Write(*.py)",</span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"hooks": [{</span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"type": "command",</span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"command": "python -m black $file"</span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp}]</span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp}]</span></div><div><span class="line-val">&nbsp;&nbsp}</span></div><div><span class="line-val">}</span></div><div><span class="line-comment"># .py 保存時に black 自動フォーマット</span></div></div></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">💻</span><span class="card-title">IDE統合 <span class="tag tag-new">NEW</span></span></div><div class="card-body"><div class="code-block"><div><span class="line-comment"># VSCode / Cursor 統合</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">/ide</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># エディタ内でClaudeを呼び出し</span></div><div><span class="line-comment"># - コード選択 → 右クリック → "Ask Claude"</span></div><div><span class="line-comment"># - インラインコメントから質問</span></div><div><span class="line-comment"># - ターミナル統合</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># JetBrains統合（IntelliJ, PyCharm等）</span></div><div><span class="line-comment"># プラグイン経由でClaude Code呼び出し</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># Vim/Neovim統合</span></div><div><span class="line-comment"># シェルコマンド経由で連携可能</span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="section-label">実践的なプロンプト例</div><div class="grid" style="margin-bottom:16px"><div class="card grid-wide"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">💡</span><span class="card-title">よく使うプロンプトパターン</span></div><div class="card-body"><div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap:8px;"><div class="cmd-item has-desc"><code><span class="str">"このコードベースを理解して"</span></code><div class="desc">プロジェクト全体の把握（最初に実行）</div></div><div class="cmd-item has-desc"><code><span class="str">"バグを修正して、テストも更新して"</span></code><div class="desc">修正 + テスト更新を一括指示</div></div><div class="cmd-item has-desc"><code><span class="str">"PRのdiffをレビューしてセキュリティ観点で"</span></code><div class="desc">専門的なコードレビュー</div></div><div class="cmd-item has-desc"><code><span class="str">"リファクタリングして、既存テストが通ることを確認して"</span></code><div class="desc">安全なリファクタリング指示</div></div><div class="cmd-item has-desc"><code><span class="str">"このエラーの根本原因を特定して修正案を3つ出して"</span></code><div class="desc">複数の解決策を比較検討</div></div><div class="cmd-item has-desc"><code><span class="str">"変更前にチェックポイントを作成してから実行して"</span></code><div class="desc">安全な実験的変更</div></div><div class="cmd-item has-desc"><code><span class="str">"まず計画を立ててから実装して"</span></code><div class="desc">Plan Mode - 大規模タスクを段階的に分解</div></div><div class="cmd-item has-desc"><code><span class="str">"ステップバイステップで進めて、各ステップで確認させて"</span></code><div class="desc">段階的な実行と確認</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="section-label">コスト最適化 &amp; パフォーマンス</div><div class="grid" style="margin-bottom:16px"><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">💰</span><span class="card-title">プロンプトキャッシュ活用</span></div><div class="card-body"><div class="code-block"><div><span class="line-comment"># CLAUDE.md に大量のコンテキストを記載</span></div><div><span class="line-comment"># 初回: 通常料金</span></div><div><span class="line-comment"># 2回目以降: キャッシュヒットで90%削減</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment">## プロジェクト構成</span></div><div><span class="line-val">- src/: メインコード</span></div><div><span class="line-val">- tests/: テストコード</span></div><div><span class="line-val">- docs/: ドキュメント</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment">## コーディング規約</span></div><div><span class="line-val">- TypeScript必須</span></div><div><span class="line-val">- ESLint + Prettier</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># 5分間キャッシュが有効</span></div></div></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">📂</span><span class="card-title">セッション管理</span></div><div class="card-body"><div class="code-block"><div><span class="line-comment"># セッション一覧表示</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">/sessions</span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># 特定セッションで再開</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">claude <span class="line-flag">-r</span><span class="line-val">abc123def</span></span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># 直近セッションを継続</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">claude <span class="line-flag">-c</span></span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">claude <span class="line-flag">--continue</span></span></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><span class="line-comment"># PRに紐づいたセッションを再開</span></div><div><span class="line-cmd">claude <span class="line-flag">--from-pr</span><span class="line-val">123</span></span></div></div></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">⚡</span><span class="card-title">パフォーマンス Tips</span></div><div class="card-body"><ul class="cmd-list"><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code><span class="slash">/effort</span><span class="arg">low</span>| <span class="arg">high</span></code><div class="desc">Opus/Sonnet 4.6の思考深度を制御。low=高速、high=深い推論（デフォルト）</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code><span class="slash">/fast</span></code><div class="desc"><strong>Opus 4.6専用</strong>・最大2.5倍速・知能は同じ・プレミアム料金適用</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code>claude <span class="flag">--model</span><span class="arg">claude-haiku-4-5</span></code><div class="desc">簡単なタスクはHaikuで高速&低コスト</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code>claude <span class="flag">--max-turns</span><span class="arg">5</span></code><div class="desc">ターン数制限で無駄な反復を防ぐ</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code>.claudeignore で不要ファイル除外</code><div class="desc">node_modules等をスキップして処理速度UP</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code><span class="slash">/compact</span></code><div class="desc">長い会話を要約してトークン節約</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="section-label">トラブルシューティング &amp; Tips</div><div class="grid"><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">🔧</span><span class="card-title">よくある問題と解決策</span></div><div class="card-body"><ul class="cmd-list"><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code>claude <span class="flag">--verbose</span><span class="flag">--debug</span></code><div class="desc">詳細ログで問題を診断</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code><span class="slash">/doctor</span></code><div class="desc">インストール状態を自動チェック</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code><span class="slash">/clear</span></code><div class="desc">コンテキストが混乱したらリセット</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code><span class="slash">/compact</span></code><div class="desc">コンテキスト上限に近いとき要約</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code>claude update</code><div class="desc">バグ・不具合は最新版に更新で解決することが多い</div></li></ul></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">⚙️</span><span class="card-title">設定ファイルの場所</span></div><div class="card-body"><table><thead><tr><th>ファイル</th><th>用途・スコープ</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>~/.claude/settings.json</code></td><td>グローバル設定（全プロジェクト共通）</td></tr><tr><td><code>.claude/settings.json</code></td><td>プロジェクト設定（チーム共有）</td></tr><tr><td><code>~/.claude/CLAUDE.md</code></td><td>グローバルコンテキスト</td></tr><tr><td><code>.claude/CLAUDE.md</code></td><td>プロジェクトコンテキスト</td></tr><tr><td><code>.claudeignore</code></td><td>無視するファイル/ディレクトリ指定</td></tr><tr><td><code>~/.claude/commands/</code></td><td>個人カスタムコマンド</td></tr><tr><td><code>.claude/commands/</code></td><td>プロジェクト共有コマンド</td></tr><tr><td><code>~/.claude/skills/</code></td><td>個人スキル定義</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header"><span class="card-icon">📡</span><span class="card-title">便利な使い方 Tips</span></div><div class="card-body"><ul class="cmd-list"><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code>tmux new -s claude</code><div class="desc">tmuxでセッションを永続化（SSH切断対策）</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code>claude <span class="flag">-p</span><span class="flag">--max-turns</span><span class="arg">5</span><span class="str">"集中したクエリ"</span></code><div class="desc">パフォーマンス重視のターン数制限</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code><span class="slash">/terminal-setup</span></code><div class="desc">Shift+Enter複数行入力を有効化（必須設定）</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code>claude init</code><div class="desc">プロジェクトを解析してCLAUDE.mdを自動生成</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code><span class="slash">/install-github-app</span></code><div class="desc">GitHubと連携し@claudeでIssue/PRに指示可能</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code>CLAUDE.md に大量のコンテキストを記載</code><div class="desc">プロンプトキャッシュで2回目以降のコストが90%削減</div></li><li class="cmd-item has-desc"><code><span class="slash">/ide</span>で VSCode/Cursor 統合</c